(secondQuint)Thoratec Corporation HeartMate PHP Cardiogenic Shock Trial.

 The HeartMate PHP is a catheter-based axial flow pump designed to provide partial left ventricular circulatory support.

 This prospective, nonrandomized, controlled, single-arm, multi-center, open-label trial will evaluate the safety and performance of the device in patients with cardiogenic shock.

